Code Officiel Géographique
==========================

This module adds the *Code Officiel Géographique* of `INSEE <https://www.insee.fr/>`_ on countries. All countries except France and DOM-TOMs (and some very particular territories) have this code.

This module is used by other modules of the French localization such as the DAS2 module.
